articles.author: Al Jazeera
articles.title: Ajax vs Feyenoord abandoned after flares thrown, rioting outside stadium - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Ajax were trailing 3-0 in their home Eredivisie game against the defending champions when it was suspended.
articles.content: Dutch football club Ajax Amsterdams home game against defending league champions Feyenoord has been abandoned as fans threw flares onto the pitch and police used tear gas to disperse rioters outside … [+2599 chars]
